name: I Hub You
body:
# Projects

### Q Stuff
I write a lot of code for [KX System](kx.com)'s language [q](http://code.kx.com/wiki/Main_Page)
* [qspec](https://github.com/DannoHung/qspec) - A testing library for q inspired by spec test libraries in other languages
* [qutil](https://github.com/DannoHung/qutil) - Some utilities for q
* [qjson](https://github.com/DannoHung/qjson) - A JSON emitter for q data structures

### Other Stuff
I've worked on a few other things
* [q](https://github.com/DannoHung/q) - A Python connection library for sending and receiving data from q

# I'm a Contributor To
* [git-p4-sync](https://github.com/DannoHung/git-p4-sync) - A Ruby script for sending git changes to Perforce as a downstream (one way only)
